GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Differentiators> ;
    narr:childCount "42"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "ef1af190777ade990ed87669f4dc7a80fb471c08" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolving definition of aswritten’s competitive moat, moving from feature-based differentiators to a focus on [decision archaeology](narr:Narrative_MoneyAnswerDecisionArchaeology) and [provenance-backed trust](narr:Narrative_ProvenanceCitationMoment). The core enterprise hook remains [cross-repo, cross-platform, org-owned memory](narr:Narrative_CrossRepoMemoryEnterpriseHook), which addresses the limitations of repo-scoped tools like Copilot. A significant shift in recent months emphasizes aswritten as a [citation engine](narr:Narrative_CitationEngineNotSynthesis) rather than a synthesis engine, prioritizing specific methodology over the platitudes typical of generic LLMs. This is supported by [module layering](narr:Narrative_ModuleLayeringComposability), which allows for compounding perspectives, and [introspect surfacing](narr:Narrative_ProductSurfacesOwnRoadmap), where the product identifies its own knowledge gaps. The narrative has recently integrated [design-token extraction](narr:Narrative_DesignTokenPerspectiveParallel) as a structural parallel to perspective extraction, while maintaining that [storing the decision process](narr:Narrative_StoreDecisionProcessNotArtifact) is the primary value-add over merely archiving artifacts. The trajectory suggests a move toward treating collective memory as foundational infrastructure, analogous to [GitHub](narr:Narrative_GitHubAnalogy).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ArchaeologyQueryUseCase> ;
